        {
            "title": "映恩生物首掛收報205元高招股價1.17倍 每手賬賺1.1萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">映恩生物(09606)今日登場，表現應超出不少人的預期。收報205元，較招股價94.6元高1.17倍，成交達20.3億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"映恩生物招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09606-IPO.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"映恩生物招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09606-IPO.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">映恩生物招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早甫開市即見181元，較招股價高91.33%，也是全日最低位；最高曾衝上222元，高於招股價1.35倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以收市價205元及1手100股計，認購及獲發每手股份賬面賺11040元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14856707-%e6%98%a0%e6%81%a9%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b%e6%94%b6%e5%a0%b1205%e5%85%83%e9%ab%98%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b91-17%e5%80%8d-%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba1-1%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
